      "body" : "Segwit + BIP66 + BIP146 eliminate third party malleability for 99% of transactions. ANYONECANPAY reopens the vulnerability.\r\n\r\nConsider an attack like this: To make sure my transactions is mined in the very next block, I pay a very high fee. With ANYONECANPAY everyone want to mix their coins will freeride my transaction by adding dust inputs.\r\n\r\n",
      "created_at" : "2016-08-19T05:55:25Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/8543#issuecomment-240934605",
      "id" : 240934605,
