   {
      "body" : "I think we should introduce another command argument for this (which implies spendzeroconfchange), instead of using spendzeroconfchange. A user who do not want to spend zero conf changes may not want his txids get randomly mutated.",
      "created_at" : "2016-08-19T10:50:29Z",
